<https://schema.acdd.dev/v1.3/date_created> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment> "The date on which this version of the data was created. (Modification of values implies a new version, hence this would be assigned the date of the most recent values modification.) Metadata changes are not considered when assigning the date_created. The ISO 8601:2004 extended date format is recommended, as described in the Attribute Content Guidance section."@en .
<https://schema.acdd.dev/v1.3/date_created> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "date_created"@en .
<https://schema.acdd.dev/v1.3/date_created> <https://schema.acdd.dev/v1.3/recommendationLevel> <https://schema.acdd.dev/v1.3/Dataset_Recommended> .
