# 
# https://schema.acdd.dev/v1.3/geospatial_lat_resolution
<https://schema.acdd.dev/v1.3/geospatial_lat_resolution> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#DatatypeProperty> .
<https://schema.acdd.dev/v1.3/geospatial_lat_resolution> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#domain> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#Thing> .
<https://schema.acdd.dev/v1.3/geospatial_lat_resolution> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#range> <http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#string> .
<https://schema.acdd.dev/v1.3/geospatial_lat_resolution> <http://purl.org/dc/terms/source> <https://wiki.esipfed.org/Attribute_Convention_for_Data_Discovery_1-3#geospatial_lat_resolution> .
<https://schema.acdd.dev/v1.3/geospatial_lat_resolution> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment> "Information about the targeted spacing of points in latitude. Recommend describing resolution as a number value followed by the units. Examples: '100 meters', '0.1 degree'"@en .
<https://schema.acdd.dev/v1.3/geospatial_lat_resolution> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "geospatial_lat_resolution"@en .
<https://schema.acdd.dev/v1.3/geospatial_lat_resolution> <https://schema.acdd.dev/v1.3/recommendationLevel> <https://schema.acdd.dev/v1.3/Dataset_Suggested> .
# 
# https://schema.acdd.dev/v1.3/geospatial_lat_units
<https://schema.acdd.dev/v1.3/geospatial_lat_units> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#DatatypeProperty> .
<https://schema.acdd.dev/v1.3/geospatial_lat_units> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#domain> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#Thing> .
