<https://schema.acdd.dev/v1.3/geospatial_lat_units> <http://purl.org/dc/terms/source> <https://wiki.esipfed.org/Attribute_Convention_for_Data_Discovery_1-3#geospatial_lat_units> .
<https://schema.acdd.dev/v1.3/geospatial_lat_units> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment> "Units for the latitude axis described in \"geospatial_lat_min\" and \"geospatial_lat_max\" attributes. These are presumed to be \"degree_north\"; other options from udunits may be specified instead."@en .
<https://schema.acdd.dev/v1.3/geospatial_lat_units> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "geospatial_lat_units"@en .
<https://schema.acdd.dev/v1.3/geospatial_lat_units> <https://schema.acdd.dev/v1.3/recommendationLevel> <https://schema.acdd.dev/v1.3/Dataset_Suggested> .
