<https://schema.acdd.dev/v1.3/license> <http://purl.org/dc/terms/source> <https://wiki.esipfed.org/Attribute_Convention_for_Data_Discovery_1-3#license> .
<https://schema.acdd.dev/v1.3/license> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment> "Provide the URL to a standard or specific license, enter \"Freely Distributed\" or \"None\", or describe any restrictions to data access and distribution in free text."@en .
<https://schema.acdd.dev/v1.3/license> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "license"@en .
<https://schema.acdd.dev/v1.3/license> <https://schema.acdd.dev/v1.3/recommendationLevel> <https://schema.acdd.dev/v1.3/Dataset_Recommended> .
