<https://schema.acdd.dev/v1.3/long_name> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#DatatypeProperty> .
<https://schema.acdd.dev/v1.3/long_name> <http://purl.org/dc/terms/source> <https://wiki.esipfed.org/Attribute_Convention_for_Data_Discovery_1-3#long_name> .
<https://schema.acdd.dev/v1.3/long_name> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment> "A long descriptive name for the variable (not necessarily from a controlled vocabulary). This attribute is recommended by the NetCDF Users Guide, the COARDS convention, and the CF convention." .
<https://schema.acdd.dev/v1.3/long_name> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "long_name" .
<https://schema.acdd.dev/v1.3/long_name> <https://schema.acdd.dev/v1.3/recommendationLevel> <https://schema.acdd.dev/v1.3/Variable_HighlyRecommended> .
# 
# https://schema.acdd.dev/v1.3/metadata_link
<https://schema.acdd.dev/v1.3/metadata_link> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#DatatypeProperty> .
