<https://schema.acdd.dev/v1.3/metadata_link> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#range> <http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#anyURI> .
<https://schema.acdd.dev/v1.3/metadata_link> <http://purl.org/dc/terms/source> <https://wiki.esipfed.org/Attribute_Convention_for_Data_Discovery_1-3#metadata_link> .
<https://schema.acdd.dev/v1.3/metadata_link> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment> "A URL that gives the location of more complete metadata. A persistent URL is recommended for this attribute."@en .
<https://schema.acdd.dev/v1.3/metadata_link> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "metadata_link"@en .
<https://schema.acdd.dev/v1.3/metadata_link> <https://schema.acdd.dev/v1.3/recommendationLevel> <https://schema.acdd.dev/v1.3/Dataset_Suggested> .
# 
# https://schema.acdd.dev/v1.3/naming_authority
<https://schema.acdd.dev/v1.3/naming_authority> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#DatatypeProperty> .
