<https://schema.acdd.dev/v1.3/program> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "program"@en .
<https://schema.acdd.dev/v1.3/program> <https://schema.acdd.dev/v1.3/recommendationLevel> <https://schema.acdd.dev/v1.3/Dataset_Suggested> .
