<https://schema.acdd.dev/v1.3/project> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment> "The name of the project(s) principally responsible for originating this data. Multiple projects can be separated by commas, as described under Attribute Content Guidelines. Examples: 'PATMOS-X', 'Extended Continental Shelf Project'."@en .
